metadata.name: Land of light
metadata.description:
With a dipping temperature and a tough trek, we were mesmerized by the view offered by the top storey of Gompa that made us forget all the hassles that we went through to take this trek. The panoramic view of the palace from the shanti stupa was captivating!

Artist Name : Srivatsan Sankaran

Edition : 1/1

Collection Name : Light and Shadows
